Package br.com.codecode.workix.interfaces

Container for Markup Interfaces

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Buildable<T>
    Markup Interface for Buildable Objects
    Builders Must Have:
    Empty Default Constructor with Private Accessor Contains Same Fields of Implementation Class All With Fields Must Return {this} or Current Builder
    Debugable
    For Debug Use Only, Show Messages on Console
    Notificable
    Markup Interface for Notificable Objects
    Persistable
    Markup Interface for Persistable Entities
    Implements this for works with
    SimpleEntityConverter and AnotherEntityConverter in JSF
    Traceable
    Markup Interface for Traceable Entities
